### 3.3 — Pipeline Stepper (Horizontal Pills)

Display pipeline steps A through QC as a single horizontal row of compact pills
inside the main panel header. Maximum pill width: 80px.

States:
- PASSED: full colour, tick icon
- ACTIVE: pulsing border animation, bright text
- PENDING: `opacity: 0.35`, grey text, no border

```html
<div class="stepper-row">
  <div class="step passed">A<br>Topic Gen</div>
  <div class="step passed">B<br>Script QA</div>
  <div class="step active">C<br>Audio Prod</div>
  <div class="step pending">D<br>Visuals</div>
  <!-- ... through QC -->
</div>
```

### 3.4 — Phase 1 Review Panel Layout

The Pre-Production Asset Review panel must use a strict 3-column layout:

```
| LEFT COLUMN (30%)          | CENTRE COLUMN (35%)         | RIGHT COLUMN (35%)         |
|----------------------------|-----------------------------|----------------------------|
| Section 1: Market Research | Section 2: Title Strategy   | Section 4: Master Script   |
| (5W+H accordion blocks)    | Section 3: Thumbnail Strat  | (scrollable, section cards)|
```

- Each Section 1 sub-field (what_was_researched, who_is_the_audience, etc.) renders
