  Expanding shows the full value + rationale block.
- Section 4 (Master Script) is the only column that scrolls internally.
  Use `overflow-y: auto; max-height: calc(100vh - 280px)` on this column.
- Rationale fields always render in a visually distinct style:
  italic, slightly muted colour, left-border accent in amber.

